"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"This [public art work speaking to the growing refugee crisis around the worl](https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/goodchance/the-walk-the-most-ambitious-public-artwork-of-our-time)d is really great. I backed it earlier this week when I saw my friend Sunny back it.\\n\\n> From July to November 2021, a giant puppet of a 9-year-old Syrian refugee girl called ‘Little Amal’ will walk from the Syria-Turkey border, across Europe to the UK, travelling 8,000km to focus awareness on the refugee crisis. [***The Walk***](https://www.walkwithamal.org/) is an international arts festival meets endurance event – the length and sheer size of the challenge is capturing imaginations even before our heroine’s first step.\\n\\nIf you are reading on Mirror or via email, [click here and watch it](https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/goodchance/the-walk-the-most-ambitious-public-artwork-of-our-time#).\\n\",\"timestamp\":1620986926,\"title\":\"Funding Friday: The Walk\",\"publication\":\"avc\"},\"digest\":\"Uqx_vcV5AqG_7xv6fL850qxqiXegB8BPoFIaYl4osfI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xB8332710AB60A1B2e8FE6D775d83524C9E0cE136\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"LTl3aLSRol2QUVUD6CZDmgOh-_8_repOG-vj-b00m1o\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Q21DlwnMAzKTxzvSjREQR-eWtchCVIOEf9pQ8-_jbbs\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"3l1C8XTiyHa2EaWLLVc79p8dpjbSasoiAy2IsNCLT0WIt3gs1wwLFvcmOAFqoYbfbkCEcxq8my6zOvVIqaSTUw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xa36ed4a1f484cc32e85a01be266ff07df93d7d551959ab6f44e5cb7aca49bba22841e81a419ff9150996b75ecf4a0a87eda7e1e79898e4f8e48a13744383f7451b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on avc.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"LTl3aLSRol2QUVUD6CZDmgOh-_8_repOG-vj-b00m1o\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Q21DlwnMAzKTxzvSjREQR-eWtchCVIOEf9pQ8-_jbbs\\\"}\",\"alg